Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不飛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:00:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego Type-L嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被選中的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很不滿嘛 呆在GGP更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是基法 只是個恐怖份子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人 尾形琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單突破了GGP的防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連警察的特殊車輛都輕易玩弄的謎之Rideback少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那裡有我必須要救的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎上Fuego的你不受任何東西制約
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:02:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這祝福之光中 你無意間已經將自己的初衷改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和你是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上接你的人就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那之前你好好放鬆下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:47.46,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:47.46,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:49.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:49.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:52.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:52.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:56.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:56.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:07.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:07.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:10.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:10.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:34.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:34.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:38.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:38.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
